TY  - JOUR
T1  - General Equilibrium Oligopoly and Ownership Structure
AU  - Azar, José
AU  - Vives, Xavier
Y1  - 2021/05/01
PY  - 2021
DA  - 2021/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA17906
T2  - Econometrica
